Angular Environment Set Up


1. Download Node.js (download the recommended version)
https://nodejs.org/en/

Note: will be installed at /usr/local/bin/node and /usr/local/bin/npm

2. Run
	npm install -g @angular/cli

3. To create a new project
	ng new *name of project*

4. Enter directory of project

5. Run ng serve

6. Download ATOM text editor